                    <div class="p_badge">
                        <a href="/f/like/level?kw=%E5%93%B2%E5%AD%A6&ie=utf-8&lv_t=lv_nav_intro" target="_blank" class="user_badge d_badge_bright d_badge_icon1" title="本吧头衔3级，经验值24，点击进入等级头衔说明页"><div class="d_badge_title ">所识者</div><div class="d_badge_lv">3</div></a>
